<article class="post--single post-6078 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-fall category-gluten-free category-entrees category-perennial-favorite category-vegetable category-vegetarian category-winter tag-all-about-braising tag-feeding-a-kid tag-molly-stevens ingredients-beans ingredients-escarole" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/BlogPosting">
